</section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;"><section class="" style="vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 100%;overflow: hidden !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.75" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fX8r9RMlzVwQjGFJFB5mUMSiccicYSPhibXLpt8GWtlvpePES7hkHRUY2v4Gn0MNKyibS16qAP9MhfylhTTBsSNlIQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;"></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class="" style="text-align: left;font-size:15px;line-height:35px;;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;"><p style="text-align: justify;white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">从直管党员，到在职、流动党员，再到社区居民，星火先锋志愿服务队的成员不断增多，队伍也在不断壮大，累计服务居民上千余人。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br  /></p></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class=""><p><br  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class=""><section data-role="outer" label="Powered by 135editor.com" style="font-size:16px;"><section data-role="paragraph" class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><p><br  /></p></section><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90858" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%;display:flex;display:-webkit-flex;justify-content:center;-webkit-justify-content:center;" data-width="100%"><section><section style="width:100px;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.525096525096525" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkG0DP9w0EHrHLesEUOCVFhwVu2gziaN2g