;"><section class="" style="vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 100%;overflow: hidden !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.75" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fX8r9RMlzVwQjGFJFB5mUMSiccicYSPhibX3ianXX4Libd3BbcfylC0jjibnIY0mCiawGB7cOAicAp15AO7csSb3yfHWXA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;"></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class="" style="text-align: left;font-size:15px;line-height:35px;;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;"><p style="text-align: justify;white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">但随着新鲜血液的加入，具备特长的党员和居民越来越多，星火先锋志愿服务队通过资源整合，发挥志愿者自身特长，开展了星火先锋健康义诊服务，由两位经验丰富的退休党员医务工作者定期在居委会开展免费测量血糖、血压活动。</span></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin: 20px 0%;"><section class="" style="vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 100%;overflow: hidden !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.75" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fX8r9RMlzVwQjGFJFB5mUMSiccicYSPhibXqnqpJwo86VEMsZ5QEibkicpWzeGIqWqhBJciaOCRHx9f2PY3icUpvRoWww/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;"></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class="" style="text-align: left;font-size:15px;line-height:35px;;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;"><p style="text-align: justify;white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">除此之外，还结合居民需求，开设了很多惠民课堂，如书法课、国画课、中式面点、西式烘焙等，都是由星火先锋志愿服务队的党员或居民志愿者担任老师，免费教授社区居民各类课程，这些服务都受到了居民们的一致好评。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br  /></p></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class=""><p><br  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class=""><p><br  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section data-role="outer" label="Powered by 135editor.com" style="font-size:16px;"><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90858" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%;display:flex;display:-webkit-flex;justify-content:center;-webkit-justify-content:center;" data-width="100%"><section><section style="width:100px;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.525096525096525" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkG0DP9w0EHrHLesEUOCVFhwVu2gziaN2gn4EghASczQQ8VZCx0QicYAfLv5vj6NnzBAp8SOtqIicOYA/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="259" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;"></section></section><section style="margin-left:10px;"><section style="font-size:18px;color:#e60b0b;font-weight:bold;"><p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">从被动组织到主动参与</span></p><p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">服务意识不断提高</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;margin: 10px 0% -15px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><br  /></p></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;"><br  /></p><section class="" style="display: inline-block;width: 95%;vertical-align: top;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class="" style="text-align: justify;font-size:15px;line-height:35px;;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;"><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">星火先锋志愿服务队在运转初期开展的志愿服务大都为集中行动，由党员带动居民志愿者一起参与，并以完成服务为目标，没有充分发挥志愿者个人特长，也没有真正将志愿者的服务热情和积极性调动起来。因此，在后期的服务过程中，星火先锋志愿服务队不断探索新的工作方法，通过提升志愿者自身素质及深化服务内容来提高志愿者的主动参与率；同时，挖掘每个志愿者的特长，发挥每个志愿者的优势，让他们能够在服务中实现自身价值，从而提高他们参与志愿服务的积极性和主动性。在春节前期，星火先锋志愿服务队的队员们就主动组织开展了春节送祝福活动，擅长书法的志愿者负责写春联，退休医务工作者为居民免费测血压、量血糖。<br  /></span></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin: 20px 0%;"><section class="" style="vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 100%;overflow: hidden !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.75" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fX8r9RMlzVwQjGFJFB5mUMSiccicYSPhibXPuyyewV4hyLicq0x8m0ICgBNHjkfOh1V49hr4pvMkMtiakAOngGbEfnw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;"></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class="" style="text-align: left;font-size:15px;line-height:35px;;line-height: 2.2;letter-spacing: 1px;"><p style="text-align: justify;white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">还有党员、居民志愿者和社区工作人员一起上门为社区特殊人群送上手写春联，志愿者们的服务意识已从“要我做”转化成“我要做”。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br  /></p></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=""><section class=""><section data-role="outer" label="Powered by 135editor.com" style="font-size:16px;"><p><img class="" data-ratio="0.05" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvkG0DP9w0EHrHLesEUOCVFhjdibibhHY0K1eBsxbAiaAGf439vE7duPUYR1MfSLWdoMZ0y0mzybl8gNg/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="400" style="vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;color: rgb(50, 51, 54);font family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);width: 347.328px;display: block;"></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92287" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;bord